// ...
const [isFormPanelOpen, setIsFormPanelOpen] = useState(true)
```

#### Step 2 — Make the form panel div collapsible

Find the desktop form panel div (line 77–111). Change it from a fixed `w-[380px]` div to an animated collapsible:

